OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 20 JUN
OL,4,CEVENTS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1990FArchie McPherson commentates on
OL,7,Fa football match for BBC Scotland for
OL,8,Fthe final time.
OL,9,
OL,10,FHe would later commentate for Eurosport
OL,11,Fand STV.
OL,12,
OL,13,FHe was on standby for STV to cover
OL,14,FScotland games in the 1998 World Cup,
OL,15,Fas Gerry McNee suffered a heart scare
OL,16,Fearlier in the year.
OL,17,
OL,18,FBut Gerry recovered and did the games
OL,19,Ffor STV, while Archie commentated on
OL,20,Fgames for Eurosport.
OL,21,
